{"tid":798093,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【珠光寶氣】陳霽平46歲仲Keep得好好　中大碩士畢業仲做埋助教","createTime":"2018-08-29T04:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T03:08:20.000Z","uid":130626,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d343c01eaefc558a4a5b192aa21b372d9ab68a43","tid":798093,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1801691/org/43539a9f122406f7cda8881c42dedfad.jpg/3Cz9ZdV0EbtmoBxXPYMcRC20HIFkQCuVTQQ_cE0EP3A?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1801691%2Forg%2F43539a9f122406f7cda8881c42dedfad.jpg%2F3Cz9ZdV0EbtmoBxXPYMcRC20HIFkQCuVTQQ_cE0EP3A%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=85cdfd14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1801735/org/6d88bf24187e1ddb3fafd50ae14cf524.jpg/rqvpd3PCeJbW-uUub6wZzppshlMpiFKNt__tR7f_7Uc?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1801735%2Forg%2F6d88bf24187e1ddb3fafd50ae14cf524.jpg%2Frqvpd3PCeJbW-uUub6wZzppshlMpiFKNt__tR7f_7Uc%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=1ef921e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《珠光寶氣》播了一星期有多，這套影星雲集的劇集，在頭一個星期已經重重好戲，尤其是蔡少芬間中的爆發性，特別有力。<br />\n<br />\n《珠光寶氣》裡面，蔡少芬飾演三妹康雅思，有一位靚女助理Sharon，演員是暫時沒有再拍戲的陳霽平Maria。陳霽平在2008年，拍完《珠光寶氣》後便離開了TVB，過了幾年自由人身份，便去了港視拍了三套劇集，不過由於牌照問題，也只是逗留了一段短暫的日子。<br />\n<br />\n陳霽平自港視後，除了在港台拍過一部《我的家庭醫生 II》外，便沒有其他新的影視作品，但並不等於她退出了娛樂圈，間中都會出席一些品牌活動。而家現在的工作，是一名補習教師，原來陳霽平的英文水平相當之高，曾經出書教導英文，亦試過出英文發聲app。在小學畢業後她便移居美國，大學時期去加拿大留流，回流香港後亦於香港中文大學修讀傳理系碩士，更擔任過中大傳理系助教，絕對是一名高學歷女強人。在1995年參港港姐入行的她，曾坦言一開始只是為了完成大學功課才參選體驗，想不到最終卻加入了娛樂圈。<br />\n<br />\n現年46歲的她，在臉上並沒有留下太多歲月的痕跡，依然是美艷動人，是娛樂圈中又一名「凍齡美女」。在她自己的憶述中提及過，名字中的「霽」，這個比較少見的字是由爸爸親自為她改的，「霽」這個字含有雨過天晴的意思，陳的父親希望她為這個世界帶來「雨過天晴」，亦即是和平。"},{"pid":"f06da49864a5ff2bbea3c2db9cd0bf8c4b0c6ff4","tid":798093,"uid":132587,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:50:22.000Z","msg":"好想一路罰抄佢個名一路屌到佢停經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17308c0b85ada88bad9b71dcc3f820fc782cd96f","tid":798093,"uid":51041,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:50:59.000Z","msg":"條女勁撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d641835869aeeb22d65fc4a896e410c9f9466167","tid":798093,"uid":40272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:51:39.000Z","msg":"西梅汁"},{"pid":"6e3bbd808bf7086643b89cf005a1e075ea49c2b6","tid":798093,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:51:43.000Z","msg":"好靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aebd9443a85df6e004a51d98a457a760437a43d2","tid":798093,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b592e49eea96e2457b5a2022e08b80cbd53d382","tid":798093,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:52:35.000Z","msg":"大把<br />\n正!"},{"pid":"b380849e1f849530fb92224b0c08af7c98b2f830","tid":798093,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"片石轉身"},{"pid":"988afb1f3d7ad8d01b5a84aa9aad8fa4e51412cf","tid":798093,"uid":1430,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T06:00:07.000Z","msg":"寶嬋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ce7d9a1a57d6d98f394bbe427b92f44819039a","tid":798093,"uid":147242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/